OL,3,CDriving instructor banned for drink-
OL,4,Cdriving after crashing on way to lesson
OL,6,FA driving instructor was four times
OL,7,Fover the limit when he was arrested on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of drink-driving while on
OL,9,Fhis way to pick up a pupil for a
OL,10,Flesson.
OL,12,FDyfed-Powys Police police said it
OL,13,Freceived a report of a single-vehicle
OL,14,Fcollision on the A484 between Pembrey
OL,15,Fto Kidwelly in Carmarthenshire at
OL,16,Faround 7:38am on Friday, 20 February,
OL,17,Fafter a car was found in a roadside
OL,18,Fditch.
