OL,3,CDriving instructor banned for drink-
OL,4,Cdriving after crashing on way to lesson
OL,6,FThe force said the driver, 54-year-old
OL,7,FTimothy Howells, a local driving
OL,8,Finstructor from Burry Port, appeared
OL,9,Fheavily intoxicated to officers and
OL,10,Fprovided an initial roadside breath
OL,11,Ftest reading of 110 and was arrested
OL,12,Fon suspicion of drink-driving.
OL,14,FA police statement said: "A short time
OL,15,Flater while in custody, Howells
OL,16,Fprovided a second evidential breath
OL,17,Ftest reading of 132 ` four times over
OL,18,Fthe limit.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
