FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1772055663
OL,3,CDriving instructor banned for drink-
OL,4,Cdriving after crashing on way to lesson
OL,6,F"In interview, Howells admitted that
OL,7,Fwhen he was arrested by officers, he
OL,8,Fwas on his way to collect a pupil for
OL,9,Fa driving lesson.
OL,11,F"After appearing in Llanelli
OL,12,FMagistrates' Court, Howells has been
OL,13,Fgiven an eight-week custodial
OL,14,Fsentence, suspended for 18 months."
OL,16,FHe was also ordered to engage with an
OL,17,Falcohol treatment programme for nine
OL,18,Fmonths and told to he must carry out
OL,19,F100 hours of unpaid work within 12
OL,20,Fmonths.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
