OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1772055663
OL,3,CDriving instructor banned for drink-
OL,4,Cdriving after crashing on way to lesson
OL,6,FHowells was also banned from driving
OL,7,Ffor 30 months, which will be reduced
OL,8,Fby 30 weeks on completion of a driving
OL,9,Fcourse.
OL,11,FThe legal alcohol limit in Wales,
OL,12,FEngland and Northern Ireland for
OL,13,Fdriving is 80 milligrams of alcohol
OL,14,Fper 100 millilitres of blood or 35
OL,15,Fmicrograms of alcohol per 100
OL,16,Fmillilitres of breath.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/5
