OL,3,CDriving instructor banned for drink-
OL,4,Cdriving after crashing on way to lesson
OL,6,FChef Inspector Christina Fraser, of
OL,7,FDyfed-Powys Police, said: "Mr Howells
OL,8,Fwas operating in a position of great
OL,9,Ftrust and responsibility; Roads
OL,10,FPolicing officers have worked quickly
OL,11,Fin conjunction with colleagues, CPS
OL,12,Fand the DVSA, to ensure learner
OL,13,Fdrivers and other road users have been
OL,14,Fsafeguarded from an individual who
OL,15,Fpresented a serious risk of harm."
